  "content": {
    "visible_text": "{\"id\":4542,\"date\":\"2020-05-06T08:41:20\",\"date_gmt\":\"2020-05-06T15:41:20\",\"guid\":{\"rendered\":\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/?page_id=4542\"},\"modified\":\"2023-09-11T14:17:43\",\"modified_gmt\":\"2023-09-11T21:17:43\",\"slug\":\"teens-distance-learning\",\"status\":\"publish\",\"type\":\"page\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/teens-martial-arts\\/teens-distance-learning\\/\",\"title\":{\"rendered\":\"Distance-learning resources\"},\"content\":{\"rendered\":\"\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Teens Program, ages 10\\u201314<\\/h4>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\"><em>Forms curriculum<\\/em><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">The following forms lessons were filmed during an online Forms Seminar\\u00a0 on May 23, 2020. <\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">These distance-learning resources were developed during the Shelter-in-Place ordinances of the 2020 Covid-19 pandemic. They don&#8217;t function as replacements to our in-person classes, but remain available for our students who would like to do supplemental martial arts at home. <\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">To view the written steps to each form, short videos of each form as it is to be performed, and the techniques learned at each rank, please click through the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/teens-martial-arts\\/curriculum\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">Teens Curriculum<\\/a> page, choosing the belt your student is *<em>currently<\\/em>* wearing.<\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">View a big-picture overview of the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/06\\/teens_curriculum_poster.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">Teens Program rank belt curriculum<\\/a> here. Consider downloading and printing it for visual motivation!<\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">*<em>Below the forms lessons are a collection of hour-long classes that begin with a 30 minute warmups\\/stretching, and include a 30 minute martial arts lesson. These videos are intended to support students who cannot make it to the regularly-scheduled daily Zoom classes, or would like extra practice.&nbsp;<\\/em><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Basic Form: White Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/1mZV81-ph4U?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Chon-Ji Hyung: Yellow Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/aDTWTdZBQ8I?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\"><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Gravity: High Yellow Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/7BjZkGH14Nw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\"><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Terra Moto: Green Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/MLHid0GBMYc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\"><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Riverbed: High Green Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/kB3w9xtLywM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\"><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Attitude: Blue Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/Uqp21feIbok?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Teen Classes<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">Below is a collection of one-hour-long classes that each begin with a 30 minute warmup\\/stretching session, followed by a 30 minute martial arts lesson. These videos are intended to support students with continued practice during times they are not able to make it to the Dojo, such as vacations or quarantine periods.&nbsp;The videos are recordings of live Zoom classes broadcast from the San Francisco Dojo during Spring 2020, when we were closed due to the COVID-19 pandemic.<\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/1Qj7PnlhSV8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/ej3O7Fop7hw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/2dhIrs68V8w?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/GDMhsHdLN0s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<hr class=\\\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\\\"\\/>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/U3miNUozpGU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\",\"protected\":false},\"excerpt\":{\"rendered\":\"<p>Teens Program, ages 10\\u201314 Forms curriculum The following forms lessons were filmed during an online Forms Seminar\\u00a0 on May 23, 2020. These distance-learning resources were developed during the Shelter-in-Place ordinances of the 2020 Covid-19 pandemic. They don&#8217;t function as replacements to our in-person classes, but remain available for our students who would like to do &hellip; <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/teens-martial-arts\\/teens-distance-learning\\/\\\" class=\\\"more-link\\\"><span class=\\\"more-link-text\\\">Read more <span class=\\\"screen-reader-text\\\">Distance-learning resources<\\/span><\\/span><\\/a><\\/p>\\n\",\"protected\":false},\"author\":59510805,\"featured_media\":0,\"parent\":1571,\"menu_order\":0,\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"template\":\"\",\"meta\":{\"_coblocks_attr\":\"\",\"_coblocks_dimensions\":\"\",\"_coblocks_responsive_height\":\"\",\"_coblocks_accordion_ie_support\":\"\",\"_crdt_document\":\"\",\"a